# EmailJS Configuration
# Sign up free at https://www.emailjs.com
#
# Steps:
# 1. Create account at emailjs.com
# 2. Add Email Service → connect your Gmail (psathishkumar3113@gmail.com)
# 3. Create TWO templates (both with variables {{from_name}}, {{reply_to}}, {{message}}):
#    a) Auto-reply — "To Email" set to {{reply_to}} — thanks sender for writing
#    b) Notification — "To Email" set to psathishkumar3113@gmail.com — alerts you
# 4. Copy your Service ID, both Template IDs, and Public Key below
# 5. Rename this file to ".env" (remove the .example)

VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=service_xxxxxxx
VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=template_xxxxxxx          # auto-reply to sender
VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_NOTIFY_ID=template_xxxxxxx   # notification to you (optional)
VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
